<head>RAMPART</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">壁壘</item>
        <item xml:lang="och">堞</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>TOP of CITY WALL.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. Dié 堞 refers both to the battlements on the wall and to the crenels of it.</p>
<p>2. Pì 埤 is another term for the battlements on the wall.</p>
<p>Cf also Nǔqiáng 女牆</p>
        </div>
